Titolo: Adventure A: Planet of Death

Anno: 1981

Descrizione: Adventure A: Planet of Death is a text adventure from Artic Computing released for the Sinclair ZX81 (and 4K ZX80) in 1981. It was also released for the ZX Spectrum in 1982, Commodore 64 in 1984, and Amstrad CPC in 1985.
A version for Android was released in January 2019 and is available on the Google Play Store.
The game was followed by Adventures B, C, D, E, F, G, and H.